If you are just ranting and raving about not getting your epic because of your play time, then thats fine, i understand it.  BUT, you do have the option of playing on the weekends which i dont believe you do anymore.<br>
<br>
Alot of people stay up late just to kill VS, i know i have numerous times.  Ive been up till 12 midnight to kill him when i have to get up at 5 am and go to work.<br>
<br>
If you choose not to make the sacrifice then thats all you man, but why try and make others feel guilty for the things you wont do.  Why blame others for the times they play.  Why be mad at the world because of what you do and think?<br>
<br>
Maybe its not everything in the world thats messed up, maybe its you................. <p>DAYAK DAEMONSPAWN<br>
