<br>
In GD, (coldain) expedition guards con dark blue and are an easy quad...the quad trick for them can be found in another thread on this board.  *KEY NOTE* This is negative Dain and Coldain faction; however, it is positive hits to Kromrif and Kromzek.<br>
<br>
In SF, elder wyverns and some old wurms con db at 61 (a 62 druid told me about them and he said the elder wyverns were db).  Also, you can evac into SF and abscond to OT 99% of the time without aggro. Just have the spells ready. Then head towards VP.  Near VP there is an island with a dragon skeleton on it. You quad at the skeleton.  Since you never have kei since enchanters are never casting at the time you play, feel free to also tangle with mature chronos (the punks that dispel).  All you need is runspeed3, o'keills levity (helps on the pullling, don't need for the quad), and your nukes. If you get a guardian wurm ADD on a pull, just abscond.  Guardian wurms are level 60 and summon.<br>
<br>
There are just two spots. You can find other places listed in these forums as well.<br>
